<h1>Privacy Policy — Industrial AI Assistant</h1>
<p class="updated">Last updated: July 2026</p>

<p>Industrial AI Assistant ("the App") is an industrial AI service engineer application developed by Servo Coil, used to assist field engineers in diagnosing and troubleshooting CNC and PLC industrial equipment.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Chat messages and queries</strong> you send to the App, including text descriptions of equipment issues.</li>
  <li><strong>Photos and documents</strong> you upload, such as equipment nameplates, error screens, or technical documentation.</li>
  <li><strong>Equipment information</strong> you provide or that is extracted from your queries (e.g. machine model, control system, serial number).</li>
  <li><strong>Basic device information</strong> needed for the App to function properly (e.g. device language, connection status).</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>Information you provide is used solely to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Diagnose and respond to your equipment-related questions.</li>
  <li>Match your queries with relevant technical documentation.</li>
  <li>Improve the accuracy and usefulness of the App over time.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Sharing</h2>
<p>We do not sell your data. We do not share your data with advertisers. Data may be processed by third-party AI service providers solely to generate responses within the App.</p>

<h2>Data Storage</h2>
<p>Chat history, uploaded documents, and equipment data are stored securely and are accessible only to you and authorized administrators for the purpose of providing and improving the service.</p>

<h2>Your Choices</h2>
<p>You may request deletion of your account data by contacting us at the email below.</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>For questions about this Privacy Policy, contact: <a href="mailto:servocoil@gmail.com">servocoil@gmail.com</a></p>

